  "title": "Marketing Manager - 6 months contract",
  "description": "<p><strong>Top 3 Deliverables</strong></p><ul><li>Multi-Market Coordination: project tracking, management & communications\nplan to ensure APAC regional requirements are aligned with global product\nroadmaps.</li><li>Growth Experiment Operations: Management of the end-to-end logistics for\nrapid growth pilots, including coordination between local execution teams and\nmarketing operations teams</li><li>Marketing Planning Support: Consolidation of regional budget requests and\ngoal-setting data to support the annual planning process and global advocacy\nefforts.</li></ul><p>\n<strong>Top 4 Skills</strong></p><ul><li>Cross-Functional Coordination: Navigating complex cross-functional roadmaps\nand aligning stakeholders across different time zones.</li><li>\nStakeholder Management: Influencing global leadership to prioritize specific\nregional needs in a resource-constrained environment.</li><li>\nLifecycle Marketing Operations: Practical knowledge of E2E churn-prevention\ntactics and CRM/Retention toolsets.</li><li>\nStrategic Prioritization: Ability to identify critical trade-offs and manage\nscope to meet tight deadlines.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>What you need to do now</strong></p><p>If you’re interested in this role, click ‘apply now’ to forward an up-to-date copy of your CV, or call Shabnam at Hays on +65 60271964 or email Shabnam.Bahar@hays.com.sg for a confidential discussion.</p><p>Referrals are welcome.</p><p>Registration ID No. R1873584 | EA License number: 07C3924 | Company Registration No. 200609504D</p>",
